{"tid":1671144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中共試圖將香港示威同極端民族主義分離勢力掛鉤","createTime":"2019-10-23T09:52:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T10:26:19.000Z","uid":183758,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0a114edb925bf5fa63209d38f45ee5cadbe5af7e","tid":1671144,"uid":183758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T09:52:49.000Z","msg":"無論香港定係加泰都同呢回事冇半點關係<br />\n<br />\n雖然都有少部分政治原因 但係加泰係經濟資源分配不公較多香港係政治資源分配不公較多 兩件事係唔一樣嘅要分清楚<br />\n<br />\n中共話國際唔支持加泰偽善 根本就係混淆視聽 無論兩邊都好都同極端民族主義分離勢力無關"},{"pid":"af7c970ea8b76f4e9a5a26faed47ab60a3cdae77","tid":1671144,"uid":172638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T09:53:13.000Z","msg":"提大家今日有咩活動 10 &middot; 23<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>19:30 英國領事館國旗人鏈</strong></span><br />\n- 英國領事館外 [以旗相認]"},{"pid":"5e9e96c80c791f286cbd070c28876684f6643746","tid":1671144,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T09:54:33.000Z","msg":"將大粒癦單嘢發大嚟搞，拖機管局、民航處、航空公司落水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1671044/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1671044/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"8d30ffda8b82590995a0b7ce5f4eca3592296113","tid":1671144,"uid":335897,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T09:57:33.000Z","msg":"加泰有經濟原因，但其實唔止。人地都投晒票啦"},{"pid":"abed1a7551576bdb5749c18bbbf7a7b4454da86e","tid":1671144,"uid":183758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d30ffda8b82590995a0b7ce5f4eca3592296113","tid":1671144,"uid":335897,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T09:57:33.000Z","msg":"加泰有經濟原因，但其實唔止。人地都投晒票啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T09:57:58.000Z","msg":"所以都話係呀部分政治原因但唔係同一樣嘢"},{"pid":"30c8ebae61f361e45831eed8fb79e709135fbe12","tid":1671144,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-2